    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on how those arguments would work against stuff like content moderation laws or preventing misinformation? I want to show that even when the government claims they are protecting people, they're actually just overstepping their bounds.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
