    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a pretty bold way to put it. But don't you think that's a bit of a stretch? Most people would say that regulating dangerous misinformation is actually necessary to protect a functioning democracy, rather than being some kind of \"tyrannical\" move. Isn't it a bit extreme to say there's no middle ground here?",
